<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>@ViewData["Title"] - Technnology Group</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/lib/bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/site.css" />
    <href ="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
        <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.5.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
        <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.16.0/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
        <script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>

        <style>
            .carousel-inner img {
                width: 100%;
                height: 100%;
            }
            body{
                background-color:#250C59;
            }
        </style>

</head>
<body>

    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light" style="background-color:white">
        <div class="container-fluid">
            <a class="navbar-brand" asp-area="" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Index"><strong><h3>TECHNNOLOGY GROUP</h3></strong></a>
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="#"></a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarSupportedContent" aria-controls="navbarSupportedContent" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarSupportedContent">
                <ul class="navbar-nav me-auto mb-2 mb-lg-0">
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link active" asp-area="" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Index">Sensores</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item" style="padding-right:210px">
                        <a class="nav-link" asp-area="" asp-controller="Pessoa" asp-action="Index">Hello!</a>
                </ul>
                <form class="d-flex">
                    <input class="form-control me-2" type="search" placeholder="Search" aria-label="Search">
                    <button class="btn btn-outline-success" type="submit">Search</button>
                </form>


                <nav class="navbar navbar-light" style="background-color:white;padding-left:30px">
                    <div class="container">
                        <a class="navbar-brand" href="https://github.com/Timoteo-M" target="_blank">
                            <img src="~/img/github (1).png" alt="GitHub" width="20" height="20">
                        </a>
                    </div>

                </nav>
            </div>
        </div>

    </nav>
    
    <div id="demo" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">

        <!-- Indicators -->
        <ul class="carousel-indicators">
            <li data-target="#demo" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
            <li data-target="#demo" data-slide-to="1"></li>
            <li data-target="#demo" data-slide-to="2"></li>
        </ul>

        <!-- The slideshow -->
        <div class="carousel-inner">
            <div class="carousel-item active">
                <img src="~/img/empresa5b.jpg" alt="Los Angeles" width="1100" height="500">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                    <h5>Não sabendo que era impossível,</h5>
                    
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="~/img/empresa9b.jpg" alt="Chicago" width="1100" height="500">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                    <h5>fomos lá, nos unimos</h5>

                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="~/img/empresa10b.jpg" alt="New York" width="1100" height="500">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                    <h5>e desenvolvemos</h5>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Left and right controls -->
        <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#demo" data-slide="prev">
            <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon"></span>
        </a>
        <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#demo" data-slide="next">
            <span class="carousel-control-next-icon"></span>
        </a>
    </div>

    <section>
        <div class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-md-3 g-4">
            <div class="col" style="padding:3%">
                <div class="card h-100">
                    <img src="~/img/sensorGb.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="...">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">O QUE FAZEMOS?</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">Exercemos nossas atividades com amor e dedicação para disponibilizar ao nossos clientes a satisfação de concluir seus projetos com equipamentos de primeira linha 
              em termos de sensores</p>
                    </div>
                   
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col" style="padding:3%">
                <div class="card h-100">
                    <img src="~/img/elablue.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="...">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">TECNOLOGIA</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">São nossas ferramentas para que possamos lapidar o pedaço que falta para da vida a sua construção.</p>
                    </div>
                  
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col" style="padding:3%">
                <div class="card h-100">
                    <img src="~/img/empresa7pb.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="...">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">NOSSO DESAFIO</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">Atender os requisitos com precisão e eficiência para o sucesso dos projetos dos nossos clientes.</p>
                    </div>
                    
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <div class="card bg-dark text-white">
        <img src="~/img/empresa6b.jpg" class="card-img" alt="...">
        <div class="card-img-overlay" style="text-align:center; padding-top:150px">
            <h1 class="card-title"><strong>NÃO SABENDO QUE ERA IMPOSSÍVEL, FOMOS LÁ, NOS UNIMOS E FIZEMOS !</strong></h1>
            
            
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card mb-3" style="max-width: 100%; margin-top:30px">
        <div class="row g-0">
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <img src="~/img/projeto_ppp.jpg" alt="...">
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-8" style="text-align:center">
                <div class="card-body" style="padding-top:50px">
                    <h2 class="card-title">CONTE-NOS MAIS SOBRE SEU PROJETO</h2>
                    <h3 class="card-text" style="padding-top:40px">Estamos sempre a disposição de uma boa prosa, e ai, vamos lá?</h3>
                    <p class="card-text"><small class="text-muted">Última atualização 3 minutos atrás</small></p>
                </div>
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Let's go!!</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container-fluid">
        <main role="main" class="pb-3">
            @RenderBody()
        </main>
    </div>

    <footer class="border-top footer text-muted" style="background-color:white">
        <div class="container" style="text-align:center">
            &copy; Timothy Berry
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script src="~/lib/jquery/dist/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="~/lib/bootstrap/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script src="~/js/site.js" asp-append-version="true"></script>
    @RenderSection("Scripts", required: false)

</body>
</html>
